  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\n**Why should this feature exist?**\r\nAllows turbo-geth to work with command `extract_csv_column` of [ethereum-etl](https://github.com/blockchain-etl/ethereum-etl), required to then proceed to extract all token transfers.\r\n\r\n**What are the use-cases?**\r\nIf you want to use the archive node as a source of data to enrich a datalake and extract data from (tested using [ethereum-etl](https://github.com/blockchain-etl/ethereum-etl))\r\n\r\n**Do you have ideas regarding the implementation of this feature?**\r\nMake it compatible with the standard JSON-RPC [eth_newFilter](https://eth.wiki/json-rpc/API#eth_newfilter)\r\n\r\n**Are you willing to implement this feature?**\r\nDon't have enough golang skills",
